high_descs: Walk forward all the way to the counter.
Pick up the butter knife under the bottle of wine.
Turn around and take a step then turn left and walk all the way to the counter.
Put the knife in the frying pan.
Pick up the frying pan with the knife in it.
Turn right and walk to the wall then turn right and walk to the wall then turn right.
Put the frying pan on the table near the right corner that's near you.
anns.task_desc: Put a frying pan with a knife in it on the white table.

high_descs: Move to the counter left of the stove.
Pick up the knife from the counter in front of the wine bottle.
Bring the knife to the toaster.
Put the knife in the bowl in front of the toaster.
Pick up the bowl from the counter.
Bring the bowl to the table.
Put the bowl on the table next to the bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a knife in it on the table.

high_descs: Move to the counter to the right of the door and the left of the oven.
Pick up the knife in front of the wine bottle on the counter.
Turn right, past the oven, and move to the pan on the counter in front of the toaster.
Place the knife on the pan in front of the toaster.
Pick up the pan containing the knife on top of it.
Turn right, move towards the refrigerator, then turn right, move to the area between the table and the trash bag in the corner, and then turn right to face the table.
Place the pan with the knife in it near the edge of the table and in front of the loaf of bread.
anns.task_desc: Place a pan containing a knife on the table.
